 | ARM            | Cortex-A76      | #1286807        | ARM64_ERRATUM_1286807       |
+| ARM            | Cortex-A76      | #1463225        | ARM64_ERRATUM_1463225       |
 | ARM            | MMU-500         | #841119,#826419 | N/A                         |
